# Working with Variables

400 @number             # declares a variable called number typeof number (it's like number = 400). you can also declare it like `400 @number`
number writeln          # writes value of number (it's like writeln(number))
number 20 + @number     # mutates number (it's like number = number + 20)
number writeln          # number is updated   
"utsho" @author         # declares a variable typeof string
author writeln
true @author            # variable types are dynamic
author writeln